"Abstract The scope of this article is limited to providing some tentative answers to some questions that are likely to interest us most as observers at this point in time: 1 What are the basic elements of the new regime on encryption in France? 2 Should it be an economic and legislative model for the rest of Europe, and perhaps the United States as well? It is hoped that once the basic elements in question have been identified, the answer to the second question will at least start to emerge."
